{
  "text": "Fluorescence lifetime imaging (FLI) is a powerful tool for non-invasive in vitro and in vivo biomolecular and cellular investigations [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Fluorescence lifetime is an intrinsic characteristic of any fluorescent dye, which, over a broad range of conditions, does not depend on excitation intensity and detected signal level.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "31740276",
